Former affiliate members===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Institution\n!Location\n!Founded\n!Type\n!Nickname\n!Joined\n!Left\n!Sport\n!Primary<br>Conference\n|-\n!{{sort|Alabama-Huntsville|[[University of Alabama in Huntsville]]}}\n|[[Huntsville, Alabama]]\n|1969\n|[[Public university|Public]]\n|[[Alabama\u2013Huntsville Chargers|Chargers]]\n|2012\n|2016\n|nowrap|track & field outdoor (M);<br>track & field outdoor (W)\n|[[Gulf South Conference|Gulf South]]\n|-\n![[Shorter University]]\n|[[Rome, Georgia]]\n|1873\n|[[Private university|Private]]<br>([[Georgia Baptist Convention|Baptist]])\n|[[Shorter Hawks|Hawks]]\n|2012\n|2016\n|track & field outdoor (M);<br>track & field outdoor (W)\n|[[Gulf South Conference|Gulf South]]\n|}\n\n===Membership timeline===\n<timeline>\nDateFormat = yyyy\nImageSize = width:800 height:auto barincrement:20\nPeriod = from:1990 till:2022\nTimeAxis = orientation:horizontal\nPlotArea = right:5 left:5 bottom:20 top:5\n\nColors =\n id:line value:black\n id:Full value:rgb(0.63,0.88,0.755) # all sports\n id:FullxF value:rgb(0.88,0.755,0.63) # non-football\n id:AssocF value:rgb(0.88,0.63,0.63) # football-only\n id:AssocOS value:rgb(0.755,0.755,0.63) # associate\n\nPlotData =\n width:15 textcolor:darkblue shift:(5,-5) anchor:from fontsize:s\n\n bar:1 color:FullxF from:1990 till:2017 text:Armstrong State (1990\u20132017)\n\n bar:2 color:FullxF from:1990 till:end text:Columbus State (1990\u2013present)\n\n bar:3 color:FullxF from:1990 till:end text:Francis Marion (1990\u20132021)\n\n bar:4 color:FullxF from:1990 till:end text:Georgia College (1990\u2013present)\n\n bar:5 color:FullxF from:1990 till:end text:Lander (1990\u2013present)\n\n bar:6 color:FullxF from:1990 till:end text:USC\u2013Aiken (1990\u2013present)\n\n bar:7 color:FullxF from:1990 till:2007 text:USC\u2013Upstate (1990\u20132007)\n\n bar:8 color:FullxF from:1991 till:end text:Augusta (1991\u2013present)\n\n bar:9 color:FullxF from:1992 till:end text