in|accessdate=15 November 2019|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=Adler|first1=David|last2=Varoufakis|first2=Yanis|date=1 December 2018|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/dec/01/liberal-world-order-new-international-yanis-varoufakis-david-adler|title=We shouldn't rush to save the liberal order. We should remake it|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2 December 2018|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=Aduriz|first1=I\u00f1igo|last2=Castro|first2=Irene|date=7 January 2020|url=https://www.eldiario.es/politica/Pedro-Sanchez-Pablo-Iglesias_0_962754236.html|title=PSOE y Unidas Podemos ultiman la estructura del Gobierno de coalici\u00f3n: cada partido gestionar\u00e1 \u00e1reas separadas|newspaper=El Diario|language=es|accessdate=14 April 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=Ames|first1=Paul|last2=Oliveira|first2=Ivo|date=10 August 2019|url=https://www.politico.eu/article/antonio-costa-portugal-elections/|title=Socialists victorious in Portuguese election|newspaper=Politico|accessdate=14 April 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Arnste|first=H\u00e5kon|date=3 October 2017|url=http://www.namdalsavisa.no/meninger/2017/10/03/Ap-har-mistet-folket-15397758.ece|title=Ap har mistet folket|newspaper=Namdalsavisa|language=Norwegian|accessdate=20 October 2017|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|author=Associated Press|date=20 July 2018|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/elections/democratic-socialism-hits-heartland-ocasio-cortez-sanders-campaign-deep-red-n893076|title=Democratic socialism hits the heartland: Ocasio-Cortez, Sanders to campaign in deep-red Kansas|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=14 May 2019|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last1=Aune|first1=Oddvin|last2=Myklebust|first2=Bj\u00f8rn|date=12 September 2018|url=https://www.nrk.no/norge/_-splittelsen-gar-tvers-gjennom-ap-1.14204473|title=Splittelsen g\u00e5r tvers gjennom Ap|agency=NRK|language=Norwegian|accessdate=12 September 2018|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Barbieri|first=Pierpaolo|url=https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/eu